------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Why GPL, and why this is a SEPARATE project from negaflow
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This plugin drives SANE (Scanner Access Now Easy). The SANE `genesys` backend
used by Plustek OpticFilm scanners is distributed under GPL-2.0-or-later WITHOUT
the SANE linking exception. To keep negaflow itself under the Apache License 2.0
free of GPL obligations, all SANE-related code lives here, in this independent
program. negaflow communicates with this program only at arm's length — via a
separate OS process, command-line arguments, pipes, and JSON — which is mere
aggregation, not a combined/derivative work.

The full text of the GNU General Public License, version 2, should be
distributed alongside this software as the file COPYING. It is available at
https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-2.0.txt
